Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心點保存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個夠了，這個還給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將來說不定會對你有用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,籐澤先生，你家裡怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每日愉快地過著是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛再婚不久而已，還未動手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還未見過你的家庭成員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的新女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次有機會的時候要找我們 讓我們也爽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要一有機會的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正在讀書中，請勿打攪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請再等一下 等一下好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你每次在準備好的時候 都會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,考試完了以後 我們可以再好好的做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次你會遵守你的承諾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彩奈...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要這樣看著我啦\N我一定會遵守承諾的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天啊！她真可愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你最好說話算話 你如果不守信，我會逼你就犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你如果這麼做 你會被眼淚淹死的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼，明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他回家了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已經回家了！ 媽媽告訴我說你要很晚才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我身體不太舒服 我剛才在地下室休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還好吧！ 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就快要考試了，不要忘了 要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我正在用功讀書，不要擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,記得一個承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彩奈，你還記得 你上次的承諾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我今天就到你那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她會出國一個多禮拜 一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,媽媽實在是個工作狂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會自求多福 你不會感到寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一場好戲就快要上演了\N而且主角是你和我 彩奈...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這話的意思是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你很快就會知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他快要來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,考試結束了，對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯，但我和小柯 晚上要一起唸書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他要過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會讓他如願的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可以到樓下一起享受 彩奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇...喔...！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是個溫和的迷幻藥 再加上興奮劑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它會讓你一個小時 全身無力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不要擔心了， 你一定會在四到五個小時內恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天一定要...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...真的忍受不住了\N好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託，放開我...求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有感覺嗎？我保證會讓你更舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黃星可以讓你的感覺比平常敏感數倍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她不在家 真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這小孩的身材真是很不錯的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對小柯太好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼快就濕透了，彩奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先用用手指頭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不！不！不！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原諒我吧，小柯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我快要射了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可是我們兩的小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,懂嗎...懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我昨天有去你那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,臨時有事情，真是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你所謂的事情指的是... 什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我今天可以過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我今天有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把它吞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用力吸吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千萬不要用到牙齒...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用舌頭，用舌頭...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們現在要去哪裡呢？ 換換口味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這很奇怪 我們不是要像平常一樣做愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在工作之外 還必須維持一些特殊關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們抱怨我 將你獨自霸佔著...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吞下它吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個這樣滿意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們等著這一刻，已經很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能再做下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的反應就像是平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尤其是和我在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由於藥物的緣故...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我下一次 可以叫你的男朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:18:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告訴他我們的親密關係 會是很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一次我們可以在他的面前做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你偷拿了我的槍... 你瘋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不...不會吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公寓大樓 發生離奇的爆炸案件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,警方懷疑是販毒集團作為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一位警探在爆炸中喪生...
